title: Google, MSDE, and CCS University to set up AI-enabled university; tech giant expands AI tools for JEE aspirants
description: The Ministry of Skill Development, CCS University, and Google launched a collaboration to create an AI-enabled university in India, enhancing higher education and skilling initiatives with significant AI integration.

title: Microsoft Turns Copilot Into Your Personal AI Shopper
description: What if your AI could not just suggest products but also buy them for you? With a new checkout feature, Copilot now searches, compares, and completes purchases - all inside the app.
